init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After the film, you enter a door and find yourself in another cinema with about five hundred people.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A man in a tuxedo walks up to you and introduces himself as God.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that your time has come, and he is ready to take you to heaven.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We have a special program for those with sudden death syndrome.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes, but if you are like most people who have sudden death syndrome, you have some kind of genetic defect.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: "Yes, but if you are like most people who have sudden death syndrome, you have some kind of genetic defect.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, there was really no point you living anymore."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "God, I am not ready for this!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I have so much left to do!"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "The job is to be the judge for all the new dead."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "What did you do in your life?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I had a heart attack while I was sleeping.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When the smoke had cleared, the new judge was gone.
